# Operator-local, per-install overrides (hardware UUIDs, experimental tweaks,
# personal notes). Imported conditionally by hosts/nixos/default.nix when
# present; intentionally never published.
hosts/nixos/local.nix
LOCAL-NOTES.md
switch.log

# Operator-local user identity overrides (git name/email, mic alias,
# workspace paths). Imported conditionally by accounts/<name>.nix when
# present. Stage 5 policy: tracked files carry no personal identity.
accounts/*.local.nix
